con|ROU|1965}} [[Marius L\u0103c\u0103tu\u015f]]\n|-\n|FW ||'''9'''||{{flagicon|ROU|1965}} [[Victor Pi\u0163urc\u0103]]\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Substitutes:'''\n|-\n|GK ||'''12'''||{{flagicon|ROU|1965}} [[Constantin Blid]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''13'''||{{flagicon|ROU|1965}} [[Ni\u021b\u0103 Cirea\u0219\u0103]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''14'''||{{flagicon|ROU|1965}} [[Mihail Majearu]] || || {{subon|60}}\n|-\n|MF ||'''15'''||{{flagicon|ROU|1965}} [[Iosif Rotariu]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''16'''||{{flagicon|ROU|1965}} [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 B\u00f6l\u00f6ni]]\n|-\n|colspan=3|'''Manager:'''\n|-\n|colspan=4|{{flagicon|ROU|1965}} [[Anghel Iord\u0103nescu]]\n|}\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[1985\u201386 European Cup]]\n*[[1986 Copa Libertadores]]\n*[[:es:Anexo:Estad\u00edsticas del River Plate en competencias internacionales|Club Atl\u00e9tico River Plate in international football competitions]]\n*[[FC Steaua Bucure\u0219ti in international football competitions]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|1986 Intercontinental Cup (association football)|1986 Intercontinental Cup}}\n\n*[https://www.fifa.com/classicfootball/clubs/matchreport/newsid=512314.html#toyota+cup+1986 FIFA Article]\n*[http://www.labtof.ro/fifa/1986/cupa-intercontinentala/finala/river-plate-417-vs-steaua-bucuresti-1-22178/ Final details @ labtof]\n\n{{Intercontinental Cup (football)}}\n{{River Plate matches}}\n{{FC Steaua Bucure\u0219ti matches}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2017}}\n\n[[Category:1986\u201387 in European football|Intercontinental Cup]]\n[[Category:1986 in South American football|Intercontinental Cup]]\n[[Category:1986 in Japanese football|Intercontinental Cup]]\n[[Category:Intercontinental Cup (football)]]\n[[Category:Intercontinental Cup (football) matches hosted by Japan]]\n[[Category:FC Steaua Bucure\u0219ti matches|Intercontinental Cup 1986]]\n[[Category:River Plate matches|Intercontinental Cup 1986]]\n[[Category:1986\u201387 in Romanian football|Inter]]\n[[Category:1986\u201387 in Argentine football